<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Request_Abstract (and therefore Zend_Controller_Request_Http) use setParam() to define values.  Zend_Controller_Front, Zend_Controller_Router, Zend_Controller_RewriteRouter, and Zend_Controller_Dispatcher use addParam() instead.</p>

<p>Since they all do the same thing, it would be best to pick one name for all of them.</p>

    </div>
