        <div class="body">
            <p>I was going to argue with this, but got to thinking, and I'm proposing the following:</p>

<ul><li>setParam(): use to add a new parameter or overwrite an existing parameter</li>
<li>getParam(): use to retrieve a single parameter</li>
<li>setParams(): use to set multiple parameters at once; will overwrite parameters if they already exist, but won't affect parameters not in the array passed to it</li>
<li>clearParams(): reset the parameter stack</li>
</ul><p>I will start implementing this in the incubator in the repository.</p>

